Apple's iPhone and other products have been officially exempted from the USA's tariffs as high as 145% 

Instead, they will likely face only a 20% tariff that was previously instituted.

BREAKING: President Donald Trump’s administration exempted smartphones, computers and other electronics from its so-called reciprocal tariffs in win for Apple (and shoppers). This lowers the China tariff from 125%.
I hope everyone celebrating Passover has gatherings full of great company, love, and tradition. Chag Sameach!
